line History|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-03-28}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Air Bissau]]\n|{{Flagicon|Guinea-Bissau}} [[Guinea-Bissau]]\n|1998\n|Liquidated<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.aerotransport.org/php/go.php?query=operator&qstring=Air+Bissau&where=101853&luck=|title=Air Bissau|last=|first=|date=|website=www.aerotransport.org|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Air Burundi]]\n|{{Flagicon|Burundi}} [[Burundi]]\n|2009\n|Ceased Operations<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://centreforaviation.com/data/profiles/airlines/air-burundi-pbu|title=Air Burundi Airline Profile {{!}} CAPA|website=centreforaviation.com|access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Air Mali (1960\u201389)|Air Mali (1960-89)]]\n|{{Flagicon|Mali}} [[Mali]]\n|1989\n|Shut Down<ref>{{Cite book|last=|first=|title=JP airline-fleets international, Edition 89/90|publisher=Bucher|year=1989|isbn=|location=|pages=}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Lufthansa]]\n|{{Flagicon|Germany}} [[Germany]]\n|1994\n|Privatized<ref>{{Cite news|last=Bl\u00fcthmann|first=Heinz|url=https://www.zeit.de/1994/20/neue-freiheit|title=Der Weg zur Privatisierung der Lufthansa ist offen: Neue Freiheit|date=1994-05-13|work=Die Zeit|access-date=2020-03-26|language=de-DE|issn=0044-2070}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Norfolk Air]] (collapsed)\n|{{Flagicon|Australia}} [[Australia]]\n|2011\n|Ceased Operations<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.norfolkair.com/NorfolkAirAnnouncement.pdf|title=Norfolk Air Announcement|last=|first=|date=|website=Norfolk Air|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210004745/http://www.norfolkair.com/NorfolkAirAnnouncement.pdf|archive-date=February 10, 2012|access-date=March 26, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Qantas]]\n|{{Flagicon|Australia}} [[Australia]]\n|1992\n|Privatized<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.qantas.com/au/en/about-us/our-company/our-history.html|title=Our History - Qantas|date=|access-date=March 31, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Ukrainian Cargo Airways]]\n|{{Flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Ukraine]]\n|2009\n|Shut Down<